{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-template-js","path":"/fundamentals/accomplishment/","result":{"data":{"site":{"meta":{"title":"Fostering Flourishing","baseKeywords":"fostering, flourishing, ","author":"David Hartsough","url":"https://fosteringflourishing.org","image":"https://fosteringflourishing.org/icons/icon-512x512.png","imageAlt":"Fostering Flourishing","schemaType":"WebSite","ogType":"website","color":"#06091d"}},"md":{"html":"<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\n<p><em>This page is incomplete in several sections.</em> It is being worked on and given the time and attention it needs. If you'd like to help write any sections, <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSefwCNdvxgpY6hQZ-FEnwmCHdZFOCD5WXwIMNeKmSDVSh9A2g/viewform?usp=pp_url&#x26;entry.1605531621=Accomplishment\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">please volunteer</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"definition\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#definition\" aria-label=\"definition permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Definition</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>To accomplish and achieve goals and aims</li>\n<li>To build competency and mastery</li>\n<li>To build aspiration and ambition</li>\n<li>To be proud of successes</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"effects\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#effects\" aria-label=\"effects permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Effects</h2>\n<p>Accomplishment and achievement have notable effects on one's brain in relation to flourishing.</p>\n<p>(This section is incomplete and requires an Effects table for a full breakdown of the effects of this fundamental of flourishing. If you'd like to help out, <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSefwCNdvxgpY6hQZ-FEnwmCHdZFOCD5WXwIMNeKmSDVSh9A2g/viewform?usp=pp_url&#x26;entry.1605531621=Accomplishment&#x26;entry.136454288=Effects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">please volunteer</a>.)</p>\n<h2 id=\"measuring\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#measuring\" aria-label=\"measuring permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Measuring</h2>\n<p>Subjective measures include the following self-assessment questions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Overall, I have been accomplishing and achieving my goals and aims.</li>\n<li>I have been working towards and reaching my goals.</li>\n<li>I have been building my competency and mastery.</li>\n<li>I have been motivated to achieve.</li>\n<li>I have been striving for mastery.</li>\n<li>I have been aspiring for higher achievement.</li>\n<li>I have been setting ambitious goals.</li>\n<li>I have been proud of my accomplishments and achievements.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tracking\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tracking\" aria-label=\"tracking permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tracking</h2>\n<p>Try to measure your accomplishment weekly or at least monthly.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#/\">// Use the Fostering Flourishing tool (not made yet)</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"ideals\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ideals\" aria-label=\"ideals permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ideals</h2>\n<p>Ideally every human should</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Accomplish and achieve goals and aims</li>\n<li>Build competency and mastery</li>\n<li>Build aspiration and ambition</li>\n<li>Understand personal potential for accomplishment</li>\n<li>Track accomplishment weekly and/or monthly</li>\n<li>Set weekly and/or monthly goals based on personal potential</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"resources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#resources\" aria-label=\"resources permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Resources</h2>\n<p>(This section is incomplete and requires resources. If you'd like to help out, <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSefwCNdvxgpY6hQZ-FEnwmCHdZFOCD5WXwIMNeKmSDVSh9A2g/viewform?usp=pp_url&#x26;entry.1605531621=Accomplishment&#x26;entry.136454288=Resources\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">please volunteer</a>.)</p>","toc":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/fundamentals/accomplishment/#definition\">Definition</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/fundamentals/accomplishment/#effects\">Effects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/fundamentals/accomplishment/#measuring\">Measuring</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/fundamentals/accomplishment/#tracking\">Tracking</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/fundamentals/accomplishment/#ideals\">Ideals</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/fundamentals/accomplishment/#resources\">Resources</a></li>\n</ul>","fm":{"title":"Accomplishment","description":"Accomplishment, achievement, and mastery are a fundamental aspect of flourishing that should be defined, measured, tracked, and fostered.","keywords":"fundamental, define, measure, track, accomplishment, achievement, competency, mastery"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fundamentals/accomplishment/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}